          "correct_option": "A",
          "explanation": "$\\frac{1 + \\cot x}{1 + \\tan x} = \\frac{1 + 1/\\tan x}{1 + \\tan x} = \\frac{(\\tan x + 1)/\\tan x}{1 + \\tan x} = \\frac{1}{\\tan x} = \\cot x$. Setting $\\cot x = 5$ gives $\\tan x = 0.2$, so $x = \\arctan(0.2) \\approx 11.3^\\circ$.",
